[Chief Executive Officer Murtuza] Kazmi has used the proceeds from the Trad=
ers Global fraud to fund a luxury lifestyle.
In April 2022, Kazmi paid $1.6 million to purchase a Lamborghini Aventador =
at auction. In December 2022, Kazmi paid $3.3 million for a Bugatti racecar=
.


