=09If you vote yes, and everyone else does, then you get $11.15 in cash rig=
ht away.=09If you vote no, and everyone else does, then you don=E2=80=99t g=
et $11.15 in cash, the Rithm deal fails, and=C2=A0maybe=C2=A0the board has =
